{"tid":2392777,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"年增48%！去年全球奢侈品消費僅中國正成長","createTime":"2021-02-03T04:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T09:16:06.000Z","uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"16662f2616546545c7cf8e9d3aa76f448b6ee598","tid":2392777,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121344/5224748\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121344%2F5224748&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrd4mdtfFL54JHswKolAMfW8%3D&h=ee74d2cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121344/5224748</a><br />\n<br />\n財經｜產業<br />\n<br />\n2021-02-02<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n受新冠疫情影響，全球奢侈品市場在2020年受到衝擊，交易額同比下降23%，但中國的市場份額從2019年的約11%增長至20%，成為唯一正增長國家。<br />\n<br />\n據阿里巴巴旗下天貓與國際諮詢公司貝恩聯合發表的報吿指出，2020年中國個人奢侈品市場逆勢上揚48%，達到近3460億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n2017、2018和2019年，中國在瑞士鐘表出口的全球市場排名中一直位列第三。瑞士鐘表工業聯合會最新的數據顯示，2020年1月至11月，瑞士鐘表出口中國市場的數量同比增長17.1%，達到了23.9億美元。至此，中國首次成為瑞士鐘表出口的全球最大市場。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，2020年中國消費者在境外的奢侈品購買比例從此前的70%下降到了30%。"},{"pid":"92016265e53903d94596210419b0f83760807e28","tid":2392777,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"走資"},{"pid":"539cf05f1a8decd750fbcaa16e76a05f87c72ac7","tid":2392777,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:43:56.000Z","msg":"走唔到資 瑞士錶最保值"},{"pid":"c4d3c31dbce8d52fb9f96c27c2e6b0ce1ce6601d","tid":2392777,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:44:58.000Z","msg":"正常經濟差 奢侈品會大跌 佢就升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bae002368165fa00653bcf6a5d77979cb617820","tid":2392777,"uid":231102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"所以就要奶共？咁同吸毒有乜分別？"},{"pid":"9da70f9dcbf338ed60fc5260855daf4c4626d738","tid":2392777,"uid":357710,"like":0,"di